				<td width="100%"><a href="viewtopic.php?p=14396&amp;sid=80e83e94cc178bb82c8f3395cd576d82#14396"><img src="templates/myth2/images/icon_minipost.gif" width="12" height="9" alt="Post" title="Post" border="0" /></a><span class="postdetails">Posted: Wed Jun 02, 2004 5:21 pm<span class="gen">&nbsp;</span>&nbsp; &nbsp;Post subject: A pretty good summary post of EQ's problems.                </span></td>
				<td valign="top" align="right" nowrap="nowrap"><a href="posting.php?mode=quote&amp;p=14396&amp;sid=80e83e94cc178bb82c8f3395cd576d82"><img src="templates/myth2/images/lang_english/icon_quote.gif" alt="Reply with quote" title="Reply with quote" border="0" /></a>   </td>
